name: DarkVeil
description: DarkVeil (VEIL) is a decentralized confidential trading protocol on Solana that enables fully private execution for spot and perpetual markets. Using an AI-driven matching engine and an encrypted off-chain network, DarkVeil prevents MEV, eliminates slippage, and protects trading strategies from public exposure. VEIL powers protocol governance, fee utilities, and network security, supporting a scalable and fair dark-pool layer for institutional-grade on-chain trading.
